ğŸ’­Reflection QuestionğŸ’­
â”Question:

-Why would an administrator prefer using CLI disk tools instead of GUI tools?

ğŸ‘‰#Answer:
CLI disk tools provide greater control, more detailed options, automation through scripting, and faster execution compared to GUI tools.

They are especially useful for advanced disk management and troubleshooting tasks.
